quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,Unabahe urugero rw’abantu bo mu mudugudu (wa Antakiya) ubwo intumwa zabageragaho
  36,14,"Ubwo twabohererezaga intumwa ebyiri bakazihinyura; maze tukazishyigikiza iya gatatu, nuko zikavuga ziti \"Mu by’ukuri, twoherejwe kuri mwe"
  36,15,"(Abatuye uwo mudugudu) baravuga bati \"Mwe nta cyo muri cyo usibye kuba muri abantu nkatwe, ndetse nta na kimwe Nyirimpuhwe yahishuye. Ahubwo mwe muri abanyabinyoma"
  36,16,"(Intumwa) ziravuga ziti \"Nyagasani wacu azi ko rwose twaboherejweho"
  36,17,Kandi nta kindi dushinzwe kitari ugusohoza ubutumwa busobanutse
  36,18,"(Abatuye uwo mudugudu) baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, mwaradushingiriye (tubura imvura); nimutarekera aho, rwose tuzabatera amabuye, kandi ibihano bibabaza biduturutseho bizabageraho"
  36,19,"(Intumwa) ziravuga ziti \"Ni mwe mwishingiriye ! Ese iyo mwibukijwe (muvuga ko ari ukubashingirira)? Ahubwo muri abantu barengera (mu gukora ibyaha)"
  36,20,"Nuko haza umuntu (Habibu An- Najar) yihuta aturutse (kure) mu nkengero z’umujyi, aravuga ati \"Bantu banjye! Nimukurikire intumwa"
  36,21,"Nimukurikire abatabasaba ibihembo, kandi banayobotse"
  36,22,Kuki ntasenga uwandemye kandi iwe ari naho muzasubizwa
  36,23,"Ese nakihitiramo izindi mana zitari we (Allah)? Nyirimpuhwe aramutse ashatse ko ikibi kimbaho, ntacyo ubuvugizi bwazo bwamarira ndetse nta n’ubwo zandokora"
  36,24,"Mu by’ukuri, ubwo naba ndi mu buyobe bugaragara"
  36,25,"Mu by’ukuri, nemeye Nyagasani wanyu, bityo nimunyumve"
  36,26,"(Nuko baramwica, maze abamalayika) baramubwira bati \"Injira mu Ijuru\". Aravuga ati \"Iyaba abantu banjye bamenyaga"
  36,27,Uburyo Nyagasani wanjye yambabariye akananshyira mu bubahitse